---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="BRUTALIST WEBSITE">
  <div class="brutalist-section">
    <h1 class="brutalist-title">WELCOME TO BRUTALISM</h1>
    <p>This is a brutalist-themed website built with Astro. The design emphasizes raw, exposed structures, heavy materials, and functional elements.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="brutalist-grid">
    <div class="brutalist-block">
      <h2>ABOUT BRUTALISM</h2>
      <p>Brutalism is an architectural style that emerged in the 1950s. It's characterized by a rugged, monolithic appearance with exposed concrete and blocky geometric shapes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="brutalist-block">
      <h2>DESIGN PRINCIPLES</h2>
      <p>Key principles include functionality over form, honest expression of materials, and a sense of monumentality. The style often features raw concrete, exposed structures, and geometric forms.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="brutalist-block">
      <h2>MODERN APPLICATION</h2>
      <p>Today, brutalist design principles are applied to web design, creating websites with heavy typography, geometric layouts, and a raw, unpolished aesthetic.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="brutalist-block">
      <h2>ASTRO IMPLEMENTATION</h2>
      <p>This website uses Astro's static site generation capabilities to create a fast, performant brutalist site that can be easily deployed to GitHub Pages.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="brutalist-section">
    <h2>FEATURES</h2>
    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
      <li style="margin: 1rem 0;">• Heavy, geometric typography</li>
      <li style="margin: 1rem 0;">• Raw, exposed design elements</li>
      <li style="margin: 1rem 0;">• Monolithic layout structure</li>
      <li style="margin: 1rem 0;">• Functional over decorative</li>
      <li style="margin: 1rem 0;">• High contrast color scheme</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 4rem 0;">
    <a href="#" class="brutalist-button">EXPLORE MORE</a>
  </div>

  <div class="brutalist-footer">
    <p>© 2024 BRUTALIST WEBSITE | BUILT WITH ASTRO</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
